quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  31,22,WE MEN JUSLIM WEXHHEHU ‘ILA ELLAHI WE HUWE MUHSINUN FEKADI ESTEMSEKE BIL-’URWETIL-WUTHKA WE ‘ILA ELLAHI ‘AKIBETUL-’UMURI
  31,23,WE MEN KEFERE FELA JEHZUNKE KUFRUHU ‘ILEJNA MERXHI’UHUM FENUNEBBI’UHUM BIMA ‘AMILU ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN BIDHATI ES-SUDURI
  31,24,NUMETTI’UHUM KALILÆN THUMME NEDTERRUHUM ‘ILA ‘ADHABIN GALIDHIN
  31,25,WE LE’IN SE’ELTEHUM MEN HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE LEJEKULUNNEL-LAHU KULIL-HEMDU LILLAHI BEL ‘EKTHERUHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  31,26,LILLAHI MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI ‘INNALL-LLAHE HUWEL-GANIJUL-HEMIDU
  31,27,WE LEW ‘ENNEMA FIL-’ERDI MIN SHEXHERETIN ‘EKLAMUN WEL-BEHRU JEMUDDUHU MIN BA’DIHI SEB’ATU ‘EBHURIN MA NEFIDET KELIMATU ELLAHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘AZIZUN HEKIMUN
  31,28,MA HALKUKUM WE LA BA’THUKUM ‘ILLA KENEFSIN WAHIDETIN ‘INNALL-LLAHE SEMI’UN BESIRUN
  31,29,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-LAHE JULIXHUL-LEJLE FI EN-NEHARI WE JULIXHU EN-NEHARE FIL-LEJLI WE SEHHARE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE KULLUN JEXHRI ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE BIMA TA’MELUNE HABIRUN
  31,30,DHALIKE BI’ENNEL-LAHE HUWEL-HEKKU WE ‘ENNE MA JED’UNE MIN DUNIHIL-BATILU WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE HUWEL-’ALIJUL-KEBIRU
  31,31,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-FULKE TEXHRI FIL-BEHRI BINI’METI ELLAHI LIJURIJEKUM MIN ‘AJATIHI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKULLI SEBBARIN SHEKURIN
  31,32,WE ‘IDHA GASHIJEHUM MEWXHUN KALDHDHULELI DE’AW ELLAHE MUHLISINE LEHU ED-DINE FELEMMA NEXHXHAHUM ‘ILAL-BERRI FEMINHUM MUKTESIDUN WE MA JEXHHEDU BI’AJATINA ‘ILLA KULLU HATTARIN KEFURIN
  31,33,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ETTEKU REBBEKUM WE EHSHEW JEWMÆN LA JEXHZI WE E-DUN ‘AN WELEDIHI WE LA MEWLUDUN HUWE XHAZIN ‘AN WE E-DIHI SHEJ’ÆN ‘INNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN FELA TEGURRENNEKUMUL-HEJA ETU ED-DUNJA WE LA JEGURRENNEKUM BILLAHIL-GARURU
  31,34,‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘INDEHU ‘ILMU ES-SA’ATI WE JUNEZZILUL-GAJTHE WE JA’LEMU MA FIL-’ERHAMI WE MA TEDRI NEFSUN MADHA TEKSIBU GADÆN WE MA TEDRI NEFSUN BI’EJJI ‘ERDIN TEMUTU ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN HABIRUN
  32,1,‘ELIF-LAM-MIM
  32,2,TENZILUL-KITABI LA REJBE FIHI MIN RABBIL-’ALEMINE
  32,3,‘EM JEKULUNE EFTERAHU BEL HUWEL-HEKKU MIN RABBIKE LITUNDHIRE KAWMÆN MA ‘ETAHUM MIN NEDHIRIN MIN KABLIKE LE’ALLEHUM JEHTEDUNE
  32,4,ELLAHUL-LEDHI HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE WE MA BEJNEHUMA FI SITTETI ‘EJJAMIN THUMME ESTEWA ‘ALEL-’ARSHI MA LEKUM MIN DUNIHI MIN WE LIJIN WE LA SHEFI’IN ‘EFELA TETEDHEKKERUNE
  32,5,JUDEBBIRUL-’EMRE MINE ES-SEMA’I ‘ILAL-’ERDI THUMME JA’RUXHU ‘ILEJHI FI JEWMIN KANE MIKDARUHU ‘ELFE SENETIN MIMMA TA’UDDUNE
  32,6,DHALIKE ‘ALIMUL-GAJBI WE ESH-SHEHADETIL-’AZIZU ER-REHIMU
  32,7,EL-LEDHI ‘EHSENE KULLE SHEJ’IN HALEKAHU WE BEDE’E HALKAL-’INSANI MIN TININ
  32,8,THUMME XHE’ALE NESLEHU MIN SULALETIN MIN MA’IN MEHININ
  32,9,THUMME SEWWAHU WE NEFEHA FIHI MIN RUHIHI WE XHE’ALE LEKUMU ES-SEM’A WEL-’EBSARE WEL-’EF’IDETE KALILÆN MA TESHKURUNE
  32,10,WE KALU ‘E’IDHA DELELNA FIL-’ERDI ‘E’INNA LEFI HALKIN XHEDIDIN BEL HUM BILIKA’I RABBIHIM KAFIRUNE